title: The Demon Murder Case (1983) - TV source inspired by a real case
description:
Demon Murder Case Based on a real case that was investigated by Ed and Lorraine Warren


its a  OLD horror thriller movie from the 1983s


I didnt see this classic thriller up and since it deals with the paranormal and demonologists.. and inspired by a real case investigated by the famous ghost hunters
Ed and Lorraine I thought i put it up.


Sadly the quality is not too great.. but its better then nothing.

it after all was a TV move recorded of analogue TV to VHS tape.. all add blurryness
and losses

I did what i could.. I used special soft to upscale it to 480p and sharpened
and brighten.


take it or leave it..

but help seed it if grab it
